--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.2.0 (2019-03-08)
F: Add support for monitoring via Prometheus node_exporter (textfile_collector)

* Version 2.1.0 (2019-01-30)
F: Add option to manage 'server.cnf' configuration file (mariadb_config_server)

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-01-24)
C: Rename option 'mariadb_monitor_mail_recipient' to 'mariadb_monitor_mail_from_address'
C: Rename option 'mariadb_monitor_mail_sender' to 'mariadb_monitor_mail_to_address'

* Version 1.0.3 (2019-01-22)
E: Improve script by throwing error message if script is executed interactively

* Version 1.0.2 (2019-01-21)
E: Improve script and reduce noise by removing echo command from alerting function

* Version 1.0.1 (2019-01-09)
E: Improve Shell script to prevent globbing and word splitting

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.4.3 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove 'mariadb_monitor_mail_subject' parameter

* Version 0.4.2 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove email information from message

* Version 0.4.1 (2018-11-27)
E: Minor style improvements

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-10-29)
F: Add option to disable MariaDB backups (mariadb_run_backup_state)

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-09-14)
E: Add 'no_log' parameter to sensitive tasks

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-08-08)
F: Add options to configure 'databases' and 'users'

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-08-07)
F: Add tasks to run initial MySQL installation (mysql_secure_installation)

* Version 0.1.3 (2018-07-19)
E: Minor configuration file improvement

* Version 0.1.2 (2018-07-19)
E: Change the default 'file_mode_mariadb_backup_file' permissions

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-07-19)
E: Change the default 'mariadb_run_backup_hour'

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-07-19)
F: Initial release
